Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从不会犯错
