Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看来气色不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不见了
