Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息是自己飞来的 我本来也没报什么期望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 为数字的波动而忽悲忽喜真是浪费人生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔福首席检察官在众目睽睽之下被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世事无常不可预料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 听说男爵和检察官大人的甚有交情？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 根本谈不上交情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男爵、莫尔塞夫将军和维尔福检察官是老相识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互利用来扩大权利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是这样听说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那只是别有用心之人的谣传吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…人总有阴沟里翻船的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男爵也最好注意一下人际关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对令媛是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能早日收到佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是博尚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是记者先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 你运气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的独家报导将会上头版头条
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们报社给重大独家新闻的价码是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙 失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于莫尔塞夫将军的大丑闻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会吃惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这次要做莫尔塞夫候选人的特辑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘算着靠私人交情打探点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问你些事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尽力而为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为父亲是如何取得这般成就的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作为他身边最亲密的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能谈谈意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正直吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同深爱着母亲一般
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲深爱着国家 为国而忧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲誓死保卫了约阿尼纳城 成为了英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到巴黎后 父亲因此升阶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪轻轻就升至将军之位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后终于能参选大统领
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲对政治的热衷是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也祝你父亲成功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这时期 敌人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后请多留神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象我这样靠小道消息吃饭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常会听到奇怪的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贿赂啊 黑钱啊 情妇什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是烦透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲和那些事无缘的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是成为政治家后可能有点固执过头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点令人担心罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真有那种事 我反而还会感动一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如：没想到还有点本事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了些废话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实今天有个奇怪的人找我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个讨厌的糟老头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象是卡德鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人和你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是废话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么你父亲在约阿尼纳的表现有假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道 我把他赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里严禁烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立刻熄灭火种
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是禁烟场所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请到指定的地点吸烟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去调查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙绝不会忘记我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约阿尼纳事件有假
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家也会有灾难降临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有请卡瓦尔坎蒂侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此前您发表了向唐格拉尔银行的巨额投资
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么使您做此决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于投资 我是全权委托给顾问分析师的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全是遵从其意见行事 如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说您和唐格拉尔男爵的千金在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是私人问题 希望您能说说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就透露一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我和欧仁妮·德·唐格拉尔小姐今晨已正式订婚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 那真是恭喜您了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 这可是大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 要是知道你在我会弹的更好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然她也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧仁妮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 我有话要和欧仁妮说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我见她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐说不想和您说话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想直接问她的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 至少告诉她我来过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧仁妮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才有人来过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是送货的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不经过我同意就定下婚约
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过 我最关心的是你的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚的是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你自己作主还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是说真的吗 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:13:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐我邀请了卡瓦尔坎蒂侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用打那么重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和欧仁妮已经完全结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和卡瓦尔坎蒂侯爵订了婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是欧仁妮的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧仁妮不会愿意和那样的人订婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是真 什么是假
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经搞不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么 我就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 弗朗兹 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生了什么 我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「人固有一死 惟各待其时」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吉之言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 我想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使为此而失去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算暂时离开巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要去Luna了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这时候去旅行是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不能和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此有了秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也就此结束吧 弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密基地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会找出真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您身体没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完好如初
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连伞都不撑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想偶尔淋下雨也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我要去宇宙一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 您乐意同行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…今天还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您无需道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这副表情 我不能放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等了您很久 晚餐已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您心中还是只有他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝先生去了新宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是打算和伯爵一起去避暑地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 祝贺的花来得让人应接不暇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我送您的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么尽出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是真 什么是假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是由您所决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有超越限界 勇往直前的觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有比任何人都强烈的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以断言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大统领选举的有力竞争者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费尔南·德·莫尔塞夫将军的公开演说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将在国民议会场举行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多名人前往支持
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,场内人气高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫尔塞夫将军 时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请上讲台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有你相伴 我才能走到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以您为荣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备车！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去议会场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开人们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和伯爵两人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却无法逃避真实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 岩窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十五幕\N幸福的终结、真实的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然后期待
